  <brief_title>Influence of IPV on GOR in Infants From 0 to 12 Months.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Intrapulmonary Percussive Ventilation (IPV) on Gastro-oesophageal Reflux (GOR) in Infants From 0 to 12 Months.</official_title>
